# CoreOps Ultimate ERP — Master Implementation Plan

> Based on the [coreops-ultimate-master-plan.md](file:///c:/Users/tirth/Desktop/Mini%20project/coreops-erp/docs/coreops-ultimate-master-plan.md)

## Goal

Transform the current CoreOps ERP (Node.js/Express/MongoDB + React/Vite/Tailwind) into the **CoreOps Ultimate ERP** system covering **16 modules**, **6 AI agents**, and **250+ APIs** — while maintaining the existing proven architecture and progressively adding capabilities across 6 phases.

