### 🔴 Architecture Gaps vs Master Plan

| Capability | Current | Master Plan Target |
|---|---|---|
| Database | MongoDB (Mongoose) | PostgreSQL (recommended) or keep MongoDB |
| AI/ML Runtime | Gemini API (cloud) | Ollama (local) + 6 specialized agents |
| Vector Store | None | ChromaDB (embedded) |
| Knowledge Graph | None | Neo4j AuraDB Free |
| Task Queue | None | Bull/BullMQ (Redis-backed) |
| Real-time | None | Socket.io WebSocket |
| Agent Orchestration | None | LangGraph / custom pipeline |

